springfox.documentation.swagger1.annotations

Annotation Type EnableSwagger


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=TYPE)
@Documented
@Import(value=Swagger1DocumentationConfiguration.class)
public @interface EnableSwagger
    Indicates that Swagger support should be enabled. This should be applied to a Spring java config and should have an accompanying '@Configuration' annotation. Loads all required beans defined in @see SpringSwaggerConfig
    See Also:
